@startuml
title UC05 - Submit Edit Prediction Sequence
actor User
participant "Web UI" as UI
participant "Prediction API" as API
participant "Prediction Service" as Svc
participant "Statistics Service" as Stats
database "DB" as DB
User -> UI : Select team for each criterion
UI -> API : POST/PUT /predictions
API -> Svc : submitOrUpdate(user, criterion, selectedTeam)
Svc -> DB : load match + assert status = SCHEDULED
Svc -> DB : check unique(user, criterion)
alt match open (SCHEDULED)
  Svc -> DB : upsert prediction (selected_team)
  Svc -> Stats : update vote totals
  Stats -> DB : update Statistic (home/away votes)
  API --> UI : 200 OK
  UI --> User : Show success (joined gold pool)
else locked / duplicate / cancelled
  API --> UI : 400/403
  UI --> User : Show reason
end
note over Svc, DB
  Gold/điểm KHÔNG tính ở đây. Khi match FINISHED,
  scoring + chia gold chạy ở UC06 (Scoring/Gold Service).
end note
@enduml
